# ML Models Directory

This directory contains trained machine learning models.

## Models (to be trained):

1. **demand_predictor.pkl** - Predicts charging station demand
2. **range_predictor.pkl** - Predicts EV travel range
3. **grid_load_forecaster.pkl** - Forecasts grid load patterns

## Note

Models will be trained on synthetic data and saved here.
Run the training scripts in the backend to generate models.
